around a small mountain ( french : 36 &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; du pic &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ) is a 2009 french-language drama film directed by jacques rivette , which was his final film before his death on 29 january 2016 , and starred jane birkin and sergio castellitto . it was screened in the main competition at the 66th venice international film festival .